column2: SELECT t.thingid, t.ndetect, d.objid, r.Sdssdr9SourceId, p.dec, r.GaiaDEC_#, p.ra, r.GaiaRA_#, r.feh, r.efeh, r.GaiaSourceId, r.per, r.GaiaParallax, r.GaiaParallaxError FROM thingIndex AS t JOIN detectionindex AS d ON t.thingid = d.thingid JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON d.objid = p.objid JOIN mydb.RRcRawData AS r ON p.objid = # order by t.ndetect
